{"tid":543975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【周庭DQ】郭卓堅入稟覆核　指選舉主任行政失當","createTime":"2018-01-29T05:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T18:46:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d6ea32bfaea68ae512a042d812ca1b75f7327c","tid":543975,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"周庭因香港眾志綱領被選舉主任取消參選立法會補選資格，「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅今入稟高等法院，要求法庭頒令選舉主任鄧如欣的行為違憲，並指鄧如欣涉行政失當。<br />\n<br />\n申請人郭卓堅，答辯人為港島區選舉主任鄧如欣。申請人指出，鄧如欣於2016年立法會選舉中批准羅冠聰參選，但是次選舉卻不讓同屬眾志的周庭參選，是行政失當。假如當日讓羅冠聰參選的決定是錯誤，申請人認為鄧當時是違反就職宣誓中擁護《基本法》的規定，亦屬行政失當。<br />\n<br />\n申請人認為，鄧以個人想法，剝奪周庭的參選資格。他亦指香港眾志的理念，是繼承「我國偉大領袖毛主席澤東先生的提倡」，質疑眾志「民主自決」犯什麼法。<br />\n<br />\n已報名參加立法會港島區補選的有陳家珮、任亮憲、區諾軒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180129/s00001/1517201291255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180129%2Fs00001%2F1517201291255&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=89d51eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180129%2Fs00001%2F1517201291255&h=d41455a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180129/s00001/1517201291255</a>"},{"pid":"ad53bed50170b56cef602de94cf34cd2a87c1155","tid":543975,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"好快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43414962b08181cd06b7ab69bc116fdd6e181f01","tid":543975,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ea7afa272e7d6ac72b0eb4099c5bf149d86cc9